text.item: What we are learning around the world is that if women are healthy and educated their families will flourish If women are free from violence their families will flourish If women have a chance to work and earn as full and equal partners in society their families will flourish And when families flourish communities and nations do as well That is why every woman every man every child every family and every nation on this planet does have a stake in the discussion that takes place here
